Name: Highway Rampage
About the game: Rogue drivers pilot a high-octane run over miles of post-apocalyptic terrain, escaping the ruthless grip of the forces that thirst for their blood. Choose your driver and see if you've got what it takes to make it through wasteland highways, dodging, disarming, and destroying your opposition! Features: - Customizable weapon loadouts - Upgrades - Roguelike elements - Unlockable drivers - Branching Pathways
